message.entry: The plot function does not work with a timetable collection. To plot data in a timetable collection, either ...\n * Use the stackedplot function, or\n * Synchronize the timetables in the collection and plot data from the synchronized timetable.
Tables are not supported as members of a timetable collection.
timetableCollection does not support the MemberShape input.
timetableCollection does not support the MemberType input.
All data inputs must be timetables.
